rows.label: tev056001_MSG0001
rows.name:
Nan great and mighty Nopon elder.
Leader of all Nopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0002
rows.name: So bow! Kneel! Grovel before Nan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0003
rows.name:
...Or at least that is what Nan used to say until all
aides of Nan gradually abandoned him. Meh!
Nan needs to assert authority with more...authority![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0008
rows.name:
Koko turned out to be good leader.
Koko told Nan about great human city![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0009
rows.name:
Much safer here than old stomping ground of Nan.
Plus way more people to sell to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0010
rows.name:
Nan went ahead and told ALL friends to move to city,
but none came. Very strange.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0011
rows.name: So sad. Does no one love Nan anymore?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0020
rows.name: Grrph! *cough* *wheeze* Nan feeling lousy these days.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0021
rows.name:
Nan tried to convince friends to come live in city,
but friends called Nan cowardly geezerpon who only
cares about own safety! *sniff*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0022
rows.name:
Nan not get it. What is wrong about leaving behind
dangers of caravan for better life with human friends?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0023
rows.name:
Young, beautiful Nopon have all abandoned Nan.
Now Nan not even have cuties to grope.
It is fate worse than death! Meh-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0027
rows.name:
Grrph! *cough* *wheeze* Nopon across Mira should
all know about illness of Nan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0028
rows.name: For now, friend can go ahead and scour planet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG0029
rows.name:
But then Nan has tiny little favor to ask before it too
late. *cough* *gurgle*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1030
rows.name: Nan hear all about Ganglion attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1031
rows.name:
How dare they invade city of kind friends who snuggle
up to Nopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1032
rows.name:
How dare they threaten marketplace where friends lap
up second-rate merchandise for first-rate prices![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1033
rows.name:
Er...uh...oops. Pretend Nan not say that, okay?
Nan never take advantage of kind, discerning friends![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1037
rows.name:
Nan knows Cauldros caravan will be in good hands
with Pisa.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1038
rows.name:
But Nan will never entrust it to Popote.
That one will never be successor to mighty Nan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1039
rows.name:
Nan would never have learned how unreliable
Popote is if friend had not helped with fireworks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1040
rows.name:
Nan will whip sense into Popote, then live out rest
of days in retirement getting tuft massages from
Nopon cuties.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1045
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh! Stupid Ganglion! Nan gave discount,
so why do they attack city while Nan still in it?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1046
rows.name: ...Meh? Friend looks mad. Because of discount?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1047
rows.name:
Nopon wheel and deal with ALL potential customers.
That basic commerce![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1048
rows.name:
Of course, Nan will have to reconsider now that
Ganglion have made attempt on life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1049
rows.name:
Maybe secret Nopon Safety Tax that Nan tack on to
every purchase needs to be raised to 75 percent just
for Ganglion. Hrmph![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1055
rows.name:
A-hem! Once upon time, in faraway land, there lived...
There lived... Zzz...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1056
rows.name: *snort* Wh-what? Where...? Oh. Sorry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1057
rows.name:
History stories from grandmapon of Nan always
dragged on so long. Now Nan automatically fall
asleep while trying to remember them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1058
rows.name:
Long story shortâ€”Nan not really remember any of
Nopon history.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG1059
rows.name:
But friend can relate, right? Who needs history?
Nan wants to live in NOW![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG2047
rows.name:
Meh... Nan very sad Pisa not here to make Nan
feel refreshed. *cough* *wheeze*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG2048
rows.name:
All Nan have is Ngogo, and Ngogo not cute or
refreshing at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG2049
rows.name:
Popote? Harrumph! Forgetful whippersnapper like
that would only work up blood pressure![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG2050
rows.name:
...But wait. Nan hear that Pisa work every night as
dancer at place for young people called "diner."
Maybe this is big chance for Nan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056001_MSG2051
rows.name:
Nan can go meet cuties of every race instead of
just Nopon cuties! Suddenly Nan feel so ALIVE![ST:wait ]
